{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2932205, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 557442, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "对国内正常生活和开放的影响真的太大了，这波让我下了run的决心，实在不敢待在国内了", "timestamp": 1636827472, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2932211, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 557442, "reply_to": 2932205, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: run吧，芝大前两天刚打死一个成都七中的学生....没觉得国外安全多少", "timestamp": 1636827546, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2932215, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 557442, "reply_to": 2932211, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: run也有很多选择，美国本来就是发达国家里治安比较差的，芝加哥又是美国大城市里治安比较差的", "timestamp": 1636827614, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2932216, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 557442, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "麻利点run，事儿真多", "timestamp": 1636827643, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2932224, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 557442, "reply_to": 2932211, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 而且比烂的话，我宁愿被偶发因素伤害，也不愿意受到来自公权力的系统性侵害（没有得到本来可以有的东西也算是侵害）", "timestamp": 1636827760, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2932227, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 557442, "reply_to": 2932216, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 这不还没毕业吗", "timestamp": 1636827786, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2932238, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 557442, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "同打算run，对局势不同的人自然可以有不同的看法然后有不同的选择，没必要争辩", "timestamp": 1636828065, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2932244, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 557442, "reply_to": 2932224, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 嗐，还是慎重考虑吧，也不算偶发因素，上一周周末就发生三十多起枪击案，死亡九人。这种还是枪击死亡被报道出来，我在国外的同学说最主要的是没有安全感，坐车里可能会被劫车，晚上周边有遇到破窗入室抢劫、偷盗的，要是算上强奸、偷盗、抢劫这些爆不出来的安全问题...感觉还是挺吓人的", "timestamp": 1636828230, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2932245, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 557442, "reply_to": 2932238, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 确实，个人选择而已，嗐", "timestamp": 1636828243, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2932248, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 557442, "reply_to": 2932215, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 芝加哥为啥是治安里比较差的咧，它是美国治安最好排行榜上前十...最差的比这哈人多了，安全无小事，嗐", "timestamp": 1636828351, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2932256, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 557442, "reply_to": 2932244, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我觉得至少去国外读几年看看，国内系统性问题很多，经济放缓几乎是肯定的。我确实不了解美国，但我觉得绝不可能向国内宣传的那么糟糕，先看看再做决定哈哈", "timestamp": 1636828461, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2932260, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 557442, "reply_to": 2932248, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 芝大周围非常差，别的学校一般不至于，不过治安确实中国没啥可说的", "timestamp": 1636828508, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2932263, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 557442, "reply_to": 2932256, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 哈哈哈没问题哇，要是安全问题不明显我也想去几年再回来，嗐主要是注意安全", "timestamp": 1636828538, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2932324, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 557442, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "每个人心中对自由、安全之类的权重都不同，去看看真实情况再做适合自己的决定就好", "timestamp": 1636829787, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2932408, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 557442, "reply_to": 2932248, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 芝加哥的安全性和芝大不是一个级别的。芝加哥downtown挺安全的，但是芝大就emmmm", "timestamp": 1636838359, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2932409, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 557442, "reply_to": 2932408, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 芝大再这样下去要招不到人了。", "timestamp": 1636838386, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2932567, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 557442, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "已经run了。怎么说呢，看原洞评论区就觉得自由等基本权利目前是被极度忽视的状态。以政府的高成本投入和剥夺普通人正常生活的基本权利来抗疫，加以大量的正面宣传，我更偏向于认为目前的抗疫政策的确是政治层面的问题。", "timestamp": 1636851492, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 11, "pid": 557442, "reply": 17, "tag": null, "text": "#556476\n赞同", "timestamp": 1636827410, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1636851494, "url": "", "vote": {}}}